circumstances.circumstancesOfRecovery: Long Haul trucker stopped over at the Stage Stop parking lot in East Ada County.  Located in the sleeper of the truck after being down for several days.  History of cardiac issues.  Contact made with decedent's step brother, a Ray Whitfield. Mr. Whitfield stated that he did not want to have anything to do with his step brother, Michael Ree and that they have not spoken in years. Mr. Whitfield stated that he could care less about the decedent and that he was honoring the decedents wishes by not making contact with him.  Decedent's Cremains are stored at the Ada County Coroner's Office.
